(A practical energy transition does not depend on a single perfect technology. It depends on) Tj
T*
(combining cheaper renewable generation with storage, grid upgrades, flexible demand, and) Tj
T*
(policies that account for local realities. The pace will differ by region because geography,) Tj
T*
(regulation, and existing infrastructure differ. Still, the broad direction is clear. The) Tj
T*
(question is less whether renewable energy has a role and more how quickly institutions can) Tj
T*
(adapt to use it well while keeping power reliable and affordable.) Tj
